# Web-App (`apps/web`)

Internes RM-UI (Next.js App Router, React, TypeScript). **Domänenregeln und Architektur:** siehe [`.cursor/PROJECT_MEMORY.md`](.cursor/PROJECT_MEMORY.md) und [`docs/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`](docs/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md).

## Pflege

**Nach größeren Umbauten** (neue Routen, neue `components/*`-Ordner, geänderte API-Pfade in `lib/api.ts`): diese Regel **aktualisieren**, damit Cursor nicht mit veralteten Pfaden arbeitet.

## Tech & Befehle

- **Dev:** `cd apps/web` → `npm run dev` (typisch http://localhost:3000)
- **Build:** `npm run build`; Typcheck: `npx tsc --noEmit`
- **API-Basis-URL:** Browser: `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (Fallback lokal `http://localhost:5112` in [`lib/api.ts`](apps/web/lib/api.ts)); SSR: `API_INTERNAL_URL` oder Fallback wie oben.

## App Router (`app/`)

| Pfad | Inhalt |
|------|--------|
| [`app/layout.tsx`](apps/web/app/layout.tsx) | Root: Fonts, `ThemeProvider`, `SettingsProvider`, `globals.css` |
| [`app/(app)/layout.tsx`](apps/web/app/(app)/layout.tsx) | Route-Group **ohne** URL-Segment: [`AppShell`](apps/web/components/layout/app-shell.tsx) (Sidebar, Mobile-Header/Nav, Hintergrund) |
| `app/(app)/page.tsx` | Start |
| `app/(app)/companies/page.tsx`, `companies/[id]/page.tsx` | Firmenliste & Detail |
| `app/(app)/companies/new/page.tsx` | Redirect → Liste mit `?new=1` (Modal) |
| `app/(app)/contacts/…` | analog: Liste, `[id]`, `new` Redirect |
| `app/(app)/events/page.tsx` | globale Timeline |
| `app/(app)/search/page.tsx` | Suche (Query `q`) |

## Komponenten (`components/`)

Gruppierung nach Verantwortung:

- **`layout/`** – `app-shell`, `nav-sidebar`, `mobile-header`, `mobile-bottom-nav`
- **`ui/`** – generisch, z. B. `modal`
- **`companies/`**, **`contacts/`**, **`timeline/`** – Formulare & Timeline-Hilfen (`timeline-entry-type` für Icons/Labels)
- **`branding/`** – Logo, Pawn, Hintergrund
- **`settings/`** – `settings-provider` (+ Trigger aus Layout)
- **`theme-provider.tsx`** – Root der Komponenten-Ebene (Theme)

## API & Typen

- **Einheitlicher Client:** [`lib/api.ts`](apps/web/lib/api.ts) – `fetchJson`/`postJson`/`putJson`/`deleteResource`, Typen für Company, Contact, Timeline, Search.
- **REST-Pfade** (müssen zum Backend passen): `/api/companies`, `/api/contacts`, `/api/timelineentries`, `/api/search?q=…`
- **Formulare:** [`lib/form-styles.ts`](apps/web/lib/form-styles.ts); Datum/Zeit: [`lib/datetime-local.ts`](apps/web/lib/datetime-local.ts); Nav-Icons: [`lib/nav.ts`](apps/web/lib/nav.ts)

## UI-Konventionen (Kurz)

- Viele **Create/Edit**-Flows über **Modal**; Löschen oft im Bearbeiten-Dialog.
- **Responsive:** Sidebar ab `md`, unten Mobile-Nav; siehe [`.cursor/rules/web-responsive-mobile-first.mdc`](.cursor/rules/web-responsive-mobile-first.mdc).
